Awp_mexico // mapped by Murf

----------------------------
What's special about it?
----------------------------

It's a fun map based on a aztec kind of map. It's fun because there are many ways you can approach the enemy. I like the way the props are placed, very strategic in my opinion

-------------------------------
What i like about this map? 
-------------------------------

The rain effect, quite frankly =)

---------------------------------------
What weapon do I get in this map?
---------------------------------------

Awp (doh!) and knife!
